replaceConfiguration.name: [MB] Implicit encoding
replaceConfiguration.description: Recommend explicit encoding in multibyte functions
replaceConfiguration.problemDescriptor: Multibyte function is used without explicit encoding and may lead to unexpected results

replaceConfiguration.name: [MB] Replace with multibyte alterantive
replaceConfiguration.description: Suggest replacing certain string functions with multibyte alterantive
replaceConfiguration.problemDescriptor: When working with strings in modern world it is better to expect multibyte characters be present, so using multibyte function is recommend, when not dealing with binary data.
